#7800
@@yThe Guard Command Hall@@N~
A large, well-marked building near @@WMidgaard's@@N central square. Stone walls bear the Guard Command's banner — a crossed sword and lantern on grey field. The main hall is spacious and orderly, with weapon racks along the walls and a duty board near the entrance. An enrollment desk sits prominently near the door, staffed by an officer ready to process new recruits.

