@@yThe Wall Command Garrison@@N~
A stone fortress near @@WKiess's@@N frontier gate. The garrison's thick walls are functional rather than decorative, built to withstand siege rather than impress visitors. Maps of frontier patrol routes cover every available wall surface, and a large sand table in the center shows current deployments. A recruitment post stands near the main entrance.

