@@yThe Harbor Syndics Hall@@N~
A large administrative complex on @@WKowloon's@@N central wharf. The smell of salt air and cargo tar mingles with ink and parchment. Stacked ledgers line the shelves, trade manifests cover the desks, and a large chart of Kowloon's delta port dominates the far wall. A registration desk near the entrance processes new members.

