@@yThe Ember Warden Station@@N~
A fortified compound near @@WRakuen's@@N main gate. Emergency equipment hangs from pegs on every wall — rope coils, fire blankets, medical kits, signal lanterns. The station has the purposeful clutter of a working emergency response center. A muster desk near the entrance processes new volunteers.

