#8300
@@yThe Road Warden Lodge@@N~
A traveler's compound at the @@WMidgaard@@N crossroads, where the major routes to Kowloon, Kiess, Rakuen, and Mafdet diverge. The lodge smells of leather, trail rations, and campfire smoke. Maps of every major trade route cover the walls, and a large route board tracks active patrols. A charter desk near the entrance accepts new members.

